Skylark Co Ltd &lt;SKLK.T> said it will issuea 20 billion yen nine-year unsecured convertible bond in thedomestic capital market through public placement with NomuraSecurities Co Ltd as lead manager.    Coupon and conversion price for par-priced bond maturingJune 28, 1996, will be set at its board meeting to be held inmid-June and payment is due on July 1, the company said in astatement. Skylark's share price fell 10 yen to 2,880 on theTokyo Stock Exchange today. REUTER&#3;